  ('medical-tech-moex-11778', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是PCR需使用的試劑？', '["Polymerase", "dNTP", "Reverse transcriptase", "Primer"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 53, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11779', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於DNA晶片，下列敘述何者正確？', '["DNA晶片是將已標示螢光之寡核苷酸（Oligonucleotides）固定於矽晶片（Silicon）或玻璃等材質", "多數市售DNA晶片上的寡核苷酸（Oligonucleotides）的核苷酸數目約為20～25個", "固定於矽晶片（Silicon）或玻璃上的寡核苷酸（Oligonucleotides）只知其序列，但無法得知寡核 苷酸在DNA晶片上的位置", "只適用於偵測基因突變，無法用來偵測基因表現量之改變"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 54, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11780', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '目前使用於蛋白質晶片（Protein chip）之檢測方法，下列何者是利用折射率改變來取得數據？', '["酵素聯結免疫吸附試驗（ELISA）", "表面薄膜共振分析技術（SPR）", "非接觸原子力顯微鏡（NC-AFM）", "表面強化雷射脫附游離質譜儀（SELDI-TOF-MS）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 55, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11781', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於雙核苷酸（Dinucleotide）short tandem repeats的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["兩個核苷酸（例如CA）連續重複許多次所造成的序列", "兩個核苷酸（例如CA）以正接及反接交錯的方式重複許多次所造成的序列", "在不同個體中，序列長度常有不同而造成多型性（Polymorphism）", "可做為微衛星標誌（Microsatellite markers）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 56, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11782', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者目前並不適用於methicillin-抗藥金黃葡萄球菌（MRSA）的基因分型？', '["Multilocus-sequence typing（MLST）", "spa typing", "Pulsed-field gel electrophoresis（PFGE）", "Plasmid typing"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 57, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11783', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關萬古黴素抗藥腸球菌（Vancomycin-resistant enterococcus）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["抗藥基因的強度vanC ＞ vanB ＞ vanA", "vanA和vanB基因主要出現在E. faecium及E. faecalis", "vanC主要出現在E. gallinarum", "跳躍子（Transposons）參與抗藥性"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 58, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11784', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '分析與人類免疫不全病毒（HIV）特定藥物抗藥性有關的突變點，常以RT-PCR增幅下列那兩個基因 後進行核苷酸定序？', '["p24與gp120", "gp120與polymerase", "Polymerase與protease", "Protease與p24"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 59, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11785', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於人類乳突瘤病毒（HPV）的分子鑑定，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["偵測病人檢體中的HPV DNA，可以用PCR與hybrid capture assay等方法", "最常以L1基因最保守（Conserved）的片段為PCR增幅的區域", "可以將PCR產物以雜交法或定序來鑑定其型別", "用hybrid capture assay偵測HPV，同時也可以區分基因型"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 60, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11786', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關病毒分子檢測的敘述，何者最正確？', '["PCR檢測人類巨細胞病毒（CMV）DNA時，也常在正常沒有症狀者的唾液中檢測出", "RT-PCR檢測人類免疫不全病毒（HIV）RNA時，也常在正常沒有症狀者的血液中檢測出", "RT-PCR檢測丙型肝炎病毒（HCV）RNA時，也常在正常沒有症狀者的血液中檢測出", "PCR檢測人類腺病毒（Adenovirus）DNA時，也常在正常沒有症狀者的血液中檢測出"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 61, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-11787', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-103-53d0563d', 'sub-medical-tech-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '絕大多數G6PD缺乏症的基因變異屬於：', '["點突變（Point mutation）", "大片段缺失（Large deletion）", "基因反轉（Gene inversion）", "剪接位突變（Splice site mutation）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:16:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "638272c1cd69", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ef9c0cdea93", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103090", "c": "311", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "醫學分子檢驗學與臨床鏡檢學（包括寄生蟲學）", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第二次專技牙醫師藥師分階段考試、藥師醫檢師醫放師助產師物理職能呼吸治療師獸醫師考試", "original_question_number": 62, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
